In [6]:
# Function for label transfer
label_transfer_init <- function(sample.name){
    # Read Seurat object
    seu <-read_seu(dir = paste0("./COPILOT_RDS_LENIENT_DR/",sample.name,"_COPILOT.rds"))
    # Find transfer anchors
    lt.anchors <- FindTransferAnchors(reference = rc.integrated, query = seu, normalization.method = "SCT", npcs = 50 ,dims = 1:50)
    # Transfer the data "final.anno.P"
    predictions <- TransferData(anchorset = lt.anchors, refdata = rc.integrated$final.anno.P, dims = 1:50, weight.reduction = "pcaproject")
    seu <- AddMetaData(seu, metadata = predictions)
    seu@meta.data$final.anno.P <- seu@meta.data$predicted.id
    # Transfer the data "pseudotime.group"
    predictions <- TransferData(anchorset = lt.anchors, refdata = rc.integrated$pseudotime.group, dims = 1:50, weight.reduction = "pcaproject")
    seu <- AddMetaData(seu, metadata = predictions)
    seu@meta.data$pseudotime.group <- seu@meta.data$predicted.id
    # Save Seurat object
    saveRDS(seu, file = paste0("./COPILOT_RDS_LENIENT_DR/",sample.name,"_COPILOT.rds"))
    # Save Anchors
    #save(lt.anchors, file=paste0("./supp_data/COPILOT_RDS/",sample.name,"_lt_anchors.RData"))
}
